description._content: I went to the opening of an art exhibition at the Judith wright centre in the valley last week. The exhibition is from female artists from outback Qld.If you get a chance pop in and have a look the work is all so beautiful, definitely worth the visit. On the way home I detoured to New Farm to shoot this scene, I hope you like it :) This image can be purchased from my website www.bethwodephotography.com.au/

www.flickr.com/photos/38181284@N06/ click Im back from an incredible trip to Iceland, 6 days of traveling and little sleep, the most amazing country i have ever visited. This was shot at the Blue Lagoon. Hope your all doing well, i will catch up with your streams as soon as possible.
